### ==========================================
### Pruebas de seguridad - Endpoints protegidos SIN token
### Todos deben devolver 401
### ==========================================

### Sin token - debe dar 401
GET http://localhost:8081/api/reportes

### Sin token - debe dar 401
GET http://localhost:8081/api/tecnicos

### Sin token - debe dar 401
GET http://localhost:8081/api/operador/reportes?estado=PENDIENTE

### Token invalido - debe dar 401
GET http://localhost:8081/api/reportes
Authorization: Bearer token_falso_12345

### ==========================================
### Rutas publicas SIN token - deben funcionar
### ==========================================

### Login (publico)
POST http://localhost:8081/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usuario": "ciudadano",
  "password": "123456"
}

### Registro (publico)
POST http://localhost:8081/api/cuenta
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tipoCuenta": "CIUDADANO",
  "usuario": "test_publico",
  "contrasena": "123456",
  "nombres": "Test",
  "apellidos": "Publico",
  "dni": "00000001",
  "telefono": "900000001",
  "correo": "test.publico@mail.com",
  "activo": true
}
